</head>
<body>
<p>We need roadmaps to help new users navigate the GT book,
depending on what they want to achieve.</p>
</body>
</html>
</richcontent><edge COLOR="#B2B2FE" /><node ID="64C40AC1-F7AE-4D3E-A064-741E153763D8" TEXT="Newcomers" STYLE="bubble" FOLDED="false" POSITION="right" CREATED="1752220953000" MODIFIED="1752221227000"><font SIZE="14" /><richcontent TYPE="NOTE"><html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>




<title></title>
</head>
<body>
<p>Personas of typical newcomers, why they are interested in GT,
and what they would like to do or learn.<br />
We can try to mine the discussions in Discord to characterize these
personas.</p>
</body>
</html>
